34
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,920
Miss Du has good taste as expected.

35
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,119
Thanks.

36
00:03:49,239 --> 00:03:51,239
On the outside, I also used some

37
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,760
unique decorations on the lights

38
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,480
and chose some matching plants

39
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:58,559
to make the whole office cozy

40
00:03:58,839 --> 00:04:00,480
and comfortable.

41
00:04:00,679 --> 00:04:01,720
How do you like it?

42
00:04:02,559 --> 00:04:04,320
It turns out that
Miss Du is really professional.

43
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:05,720
To be honest,

44
00:04:05,839 --> 00:04:07,839
I didn't expect much from you.

45
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,119
It now appears that

46
00:04:09,399 --> 00:04:10,600
I'm very satisfied.

47
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,959
It is great working with you.

48
00:04:12,519 --> 00:04:14,399
Thank you for your compliment.

49
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,720
To be honest,

50
00:04:15,839 --> 00:04:17,119
if you didn't contact me
for this project,

51
00:04:17,239 --> 00:04:18,040
I wouldn't have confidence

52
00:04:18,239 --> 00:04:19,959
to keep doing this.

53
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,480
Aren't you curious about

54
00:04:22,559 --> 00:04:24,119
how I found you?

55
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:25,760
Forget it!

56
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,160
If I tell you the truth,

57
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:28,920
someone is going to kill me.

58
00:04:30,119 --> 00:04:31,679
All you have to know is that

59
00:04:31,679 --> 00:04:33,959
someone is trying to help you.

60
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,399
Miss Du,

61
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:37,239
