62
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:02,600
Mr. Lei Yuzheng, I've earned money.

63
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,279
Let me treat you a meal.
How does that sound?

64
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:12,959
-Qunfei.
-Yes?

65
00:05:15,559 --> 00:05:16,480
Why did you seem

66
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,640
to be distracted recently?

67
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,600
Did anything happen?

68
00:05:22,559 --> 00:05:23,640
No, nothing.

69
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,640
This one,

70
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,640
this one,

71
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:42,880
and this one.

72
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,959
Ok, that's all.

73
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,600
How were you so quiet?

74
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,119
When did you come in?

75
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,399
Ok, that's all. Order is placed.

76
00:05:55,959 --> 00:05:56,839
Wait, Du Xiaosu,

77
00:05:57,559 --> 00:05:58,799
you have just placed the order without

78
00:05:58,799 --> 00:05:59,760
asking what the guest wants?

79
00:06:01,239 --> 00:06:02,519
What kind of treat is that?

80
00:06:02,679 --> 00:06:04,399
It's my treat. I've told you.

81
00:06:04,559 --> 00:06:05,799
So, you have to listen to me.

82
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,880
Is that how it works?

83
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,480
What are you doing?

84
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,720
Braised baby cabbage in broth,

85
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,480
boiled Chinese broccoli,

86
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,200
1 serving of small steamed buns,

87
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,040
and 2 servings of instant noodles
in chicken soup.

88
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,440
You might as well

89
00:06:19,559 --> 00:06:20,959
order two clay oven rolls for us.

90
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,799
Make some changes.

91
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,359
Crab meat bean curd,

92
00:06:26,359 --> 00:06:27,600
salmon nori,

93
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,200
and sashimi set.

94
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:32,279
As for drinks...

95
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,040
Why did you step on me?

96
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,959
Who stepped on you?

97
00:06:40,799 --> 00:06:42,359
Rich people like you

98
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,880
must have tried everything.

99
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,760
Why are you doing this to me?

100
00:06:50,119 --> 00:06:52,079
Aren't you also rich now?

101
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,320
You need to admit that

102
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:57,040
the large-scale project
you recently worked on

103
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,160
must be very profitable.

104
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,480
Am I right?

105
00:07:02,359 --> 00:07:03,799
What large-scale project?

106
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,399
You made that up. Ok?

107
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,119
If you are trying to
destroy my reputation,

108
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,040
I...

109
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,359
I will ask you for
mental damage compensation.

110
00:07:10,359 --> 00:07:11,399
You won't be able to afford it.

111
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,559
I'm sorry, sir and madam.

112
00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:14,119
Whom should I listen to?

113
00:07:14,239 --> 00:07:15,320
-Me.
-Me.

114
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,000
Well,

115
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:24,000
just listen to him then.

116
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,320
Forget about the drinks.
Just place order for the rest.

117
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,320
Ok, sir.

118
00:07:29,799 --> 00:07:30,760
Lei Yuzheng,

119
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:33,920
you think that you are nice to me,
right?

120
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:36,200
Actually,
I would order abalone and trepang.

121
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:39,600
Just consider yourself lucky.

122
00:07:41,799 --> 00:07:43,160
Here, Du Xiaosu,

123
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,799
try a small steamed bun.

124
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,359
Eat quickly, or it will get cold.

125
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:57,559
Wait,

126
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,400
it's my treat.

127
00:08:00,039 --> 00:08:01,679
Why did you act more hospitable
than I did?

128
00:08:01,799 --> 00:08:02,520
If one doesn't want to do something,

129
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,000
no one can force him.

130
00:08:04,359 --> 00:08:05,039
Right?

131
00:08:05,159 --> 00:08:06,640
Whether you eat or not, it's up to you.

132
00:08:08,719 --> 00:08:09,640
Just eat.

133
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,840
Are we eating small steamed buns?

134
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,440
No, they are my flesh and blood.

135
00:08:18,719 --> 00:08:20,479
Your flesh and blood?

136
00:08:21,919 --> 00:08:23,280
I finally know what animal you are like.

137
00:08:24,119 --> 00:08:25,159
Pixiu,

138
00:08:26,039 --> 00:08:27,440
who only takes things in
but never lets anything out.

139
00:08:29,039 --> 00:08:30,119
No matter how I think about it,

140
00:08:30,119 --> 00:08:31,880
you can earn at least this much
with the office building project.

141
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:35,039
You are not willing
to even take a fraction out?

142
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,119
How did you know
it was an office building?

143
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,320
Don't tell me that

144
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,320
you helped me find this project.

145
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,840
Aren't you curious about

146
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,320
how I found you?

147
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:45,840
If I tell you the truth,

148
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,599
someone is going to kill me.

149
00:08:50,159 --> 00:08:51,479
What are you thinking?

150
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:53,799
Am I the kind of person
who looks for projects for you?

151
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:56,039
I don't have that much free time.

152
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,440
I just guessed.

153
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,559
That's what I thought.

154
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,479
You are so busy as a businessman.

155
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:02,719
How is it possible for you to worry
about lower-income people like me?

156
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,400
I got it because I was lucky.

157
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,799
That's correct.

158
00:09:11,119 --> 00:09:13,000
I really like your face
when you are eating.

159
00:09:15,719 --> 00:09:16,719
I might not be able to

160
00:09:16,719 --> 00:09:17,520
eat such delicious food for a while.

161
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,880
For a while? Why?

162
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,799
I'm going for a business trip abroad.

163
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:27,200
Abroad?

164
00:09:29,359 --> 00:09:31,200
I've never been abroad.

165
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,080
What's good about going abroad?

166
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,280
Studying.

167
00:09:36,719 --> 00:09:38,479
Do you know
the Bauhaus-Universität Weimar?

168
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,000
It's my dream school.

169
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,840
Their department of architecture.

170
00:09:43,479 --> 00:09:45,000
Professor Oam

171
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,599
is my idol.

172
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:49,000
I remember that during the first lesson

173
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,799
in my college,

174
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:53,159
our teacher was holding
the Introduction to Architecture

175
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,159
and telling us that

176
00:09:54,359 --> 00:09:56,640
this book was written by professor Oam.

177
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,880
He is the originator of
architecture industry.

178
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:01,239
Ever since then,

179
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:02,559
I started dreaming about

180
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:04,840
meeting this master one day.

181
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:05,840
If I saw him,

182
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,919
I can take pictures with him
and get his signature.

183
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,679
Then my life is all worth it.

184
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,359
What kind of dream is that?

185
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,320
Just eat.

186
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:30,919
Hello.

187
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,039
Please check out.

188
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:34,320
Ok, wait a second.

189
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,359
Hello, your order has been paid.

190
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,880
You did it?

191
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,280
Who else can it be?

192
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:47,200
You finally did something right.

193
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,760
Otherwise, I would

194
00:10:49,119 --> 00:10:50,159
curse you every day,

195
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:51,359
and hope you will be single forever.

196
00:10:52,719 --> 00:10:53,479
Really?

197
00:10:54,359 --> 00:10:55,320
I'd be happy about it.

198
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:57,760
Lei Yuzheng,

199
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,719
how did I never know

200
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:02,080
that you can also be humorous.

201
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,880
There're many things
that you haven't known about me.

202
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,760
Well, there will be
lots of time in the future,

203
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,080
and you can know about me slowly.

204
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,719
Let's go.

205
00:11:22,719 --> 00:11:23,440
We're here.

206
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:25,719
I'm going inside then.

207
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:27,919
Thank you for your dinner.

208
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:28,919
My dinner?

209
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,960
Wasn't it your treat?

210
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,559
It was my treat, and you paid the bill.

211
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:34,760
It's fair.

212
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,880
Next time,

213
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,479
it'll be your treat and I will pay.

214
00:11:37,479 --> 00:11:39,000
Then, we will be equal.

215
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,280
Next time?

216
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:43,039
I don't even know
when the next time would be.

217
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,719
How long will you stay abroad?

218
00:11:46,719 --> 00:11:48,119
If everything goes as planned,
it might be a week.

219
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,559
Just a week.

220
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:51,400
Maybe, you will be back sooner.

221
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:53,479
Then, I will go up for now.

222
00:11:54,239 --> 00:11:56,039
Take care of yourself. Bye!

223
00:11:57,359 --> 00:11:57,960
Xiaosu.

224
00:12:04,479 --> 00:12:05,119
Forget it!

225
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,039
Nothing!

226
00:12:09,359 --> 00:12:10,280
President Lei,

227
00:12:10,359 --> 00:12:11,880
it's not like you.

228
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,320
Say whatever you want.

229
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:15,559
Why are you so hesitating?

230
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,039
I was wondering if you could

231
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,640
come to see me off
at the airport tomorrow.

232
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,799
I…

233
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:29,239
see you off?

234
00:12:30,359 --> 00:12:31,440
Why?

235
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,039
Xiaosu,

236
00:12:35,359 --> 00:12:36,880
we've known each other for long.

237
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:38,919
You don't really understand how I feel?

238
00:12:50,039 --> 00:12:50,799
I know.

239
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,599
It might be hard for you
to make this decision,

240
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,840
but I'm willing to wait.

241
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,599
My flight will leave at 10 am tomorrow.

242
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:03,960
I'm leaving now.

243
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,000
Dad, drink some water.

244
00:13:46,599 --> 00:13:48,039
Siqi, have a seat.

245
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:04,520
Dad, why did you

246
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:05,960
come to Shanghai this time?

247
00:14:12,359 --> 00:14:13,840
It's okay. You can tell me.

248
00:14:13,919 --> 00:14:15,159
Siqi is not an outsider.

249
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,679
Well,

250
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,200
your brother is getting married.

251
00:14:20,359 --> 00:14:23,080
He's going to marry the daughter
of Dr. Liu in the town.

252
00:14:23,239 --> 00:14:24,400
That's great news.

253
00:14:25,239 --> 00:14:28,239
It's great news,
but it's also stressful.

254
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,080
Without the property
ownership certificate,

255
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:32,880
nobody is willing to marry him.

256
00:14:33,239 --> 00:14:34,320
So,

257
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:37,799
your mom and I
took out all the money we have,

258
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:40,080
but it is still not enough.

259
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:42,520
So, I came here to see

260
00:14:43,239 --> 00:14:46,080
if you have any money available.

261
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:51,000
Dad, how much do you want?

262
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,440
I can definitely give out
20 to 30 thousand yuan.

263
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:56,520
That's not enough.

264
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,840
Your mom and I
gathered 300 thousand yuan,

265
00:14:59,159 --> 00:15:00,760
and we still need 200 thousand yuan.

266
00:15:04,159 --> 00:15:06,000
What? 200 thousand yuan?

267
00:15:08,359 --> 00:15:10,719
Since when did it cost so much
to buy a house in that town?

268
00:15:11,039 --> 00:15:13,359
Not just for down payment.
It's the full payment.

269
00:15:14,919 --> 00:15:16,239
You must know

270
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:18,080
how much your brother

271
00:15:18,479 --> 00:15:19,919
has gone through

272
00:15:20,039 --> 00:15:21,760
in order to pay your college tuition.

273
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,280
Now,

274
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:25,719
he's finally met the girl

275
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,880
he can marry and likes.

276
00:15:28,679 --> 00:15:31,640
The family of the girl didn't
ask for too much

277
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:35,760
other than a house for marriage.

278
00:15:37,119 --> 00:15:38,440
We planned to

279
00:15:39,119 --> 00:15:41,119
make the down payment for your brother,

