00:15:41,599 --> 00:15:43,640
and leave the rest for them

281
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,400
to pay back slowly.

282
00:15:45,599 --> 00:15:47,760
But on second thought, we figured that

283
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:50,520
it doesn't seem right to have her start

284
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:53,679
paying debt after joining our family.

285
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:56,359
If the words spread out,

286
00:15:56,479 --> 00:15:58,479
it would be so embarrassing
for our family.

287
00:15:59,119 --> 00:16:00,440
That's why I came to see

288
00:16:01,119 --> 00:16:02,119
if you are able to help your brother

289
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:04,039
gather 200 thousand yuan,

290
00:16:04,239 --> 00:16:06,119
so that he can marry the girl.

291
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,400
It will be a dream come true

292
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,719
for both your brother and us.

293
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:20,440
Dad,
of course my brother should get married.

294
00:16:20,559 --> 00:16:21,679
About the money,

295
00:16:22,400 --> 00:16:23,719
don't worry.

296
00:16:24,719 --> 00:16:25,960
I will try to take care of it.

297
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:28,799
I'm relieved to hear that.

298
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:31,359
Your mom will also be happy
to hear about it.

299
00:16:31,920 --> 00:16:34,079
Qunfei, it was right for your brother

300
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:36,599
to care so much about you all time.

301
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:42,920
Well, dad,

302
00:16:43,119 --> 00:16:43,959
it's getting late.

303
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:45,400
I should send Siqi home.

304
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:48,359
Let's go.

305
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,560
See you, uncle.

306
00:16:49,719 --> 00:16:51,439
Okay, see you.

307
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:00,199
Siqi, were you mad?

308
00:17:00,439 --> 00:17:01,439
Mad?

309
00:17:01,719 --> 00:17:03,160
200 thousand is not a small number.

310
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:04,199
Adding up all your savings

311
00:17:04,199 --> 00:17:05,119
can barely reach this number.

312
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,520
My brother will return it to me.

313
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,040
So, it means that

314
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:11,839
you have already decided to
lend him the money.

315
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:15,160
My brother has been very nice to me
since we were kids.

316
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:16,640
You don't know about this,

317
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:18,400
but he used to take care of me well

318
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:20,239
when my parents were working
in other cities.

319
00:17:20,560 --> 00:17:21,560
It was because of my brother

320
00:17:21,719 --> 00:17:22,599
that I was able to come to Shanghai,

321
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,439
attend university,

322
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:24,959
and know you.

323
00:17:25,319 --> 00:17:26,040
All right.

324
00:17:26,239 --> 00:17:27,920
It's your brother who's getting married,

325
00:17:28,079 --> 00:17:29,680
and it's your dad
who's asking for the money.

326
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,880
As for me, I'm just an outsider.

327
00:17:32,199 --> 00:17:33,079
Siqi,

328
00:17:34,359 --> 00:17:35,560
that's not what I mean.

329
00:17:35,719 --> 00:17:37,040
I just think that

330
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,719
we cannot even buy a bathroom

331
00:17:38,719 --> 00:17:40,319
with 200 thousand yuan in Shanghai.

332
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,760
So, there's no harm to

333
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:43,160
give it to my family to
solve this emergency, right?

334
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,800
Yes.

335
00:17:45,239 --> 00:17:47,400
We cannot even buy a bathroom here.

336
00:17:47,959 --> 00:17:49,520
But just because we cannot buy it,

337
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,680
it doesn't mean that

338
00:17:50,839 --> 00:17:51,760
you should lend this money
to your brother,

339
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:53,800
and live in a rented apartment.

340
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,079
Does it?

341
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,520
And your dad.

342
00:17:57,079 --> 00:17:58,520
He knows that
your brother needs a house for marriage.

343
00:17:58,719 --> 00:18:00,000
But what about us?

344
00:18:00,359 --> 00:18:01,000
Have your family ever

345
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,839
thought about how I feel?

346
00:18:03,119 --> 00:18:03,920
I'm sorry, Siqi.

347
00:18:04,079 --> 00:18:06,520
But there're things that are more urgent
than others.

348
00:18:07,280 --> 00:18:07,839
Great.

349
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,439
If you want to be an obedient son

350
00:18:09,719 --> 00:18:11,040
and a good brother,

351
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,319
I'm not stopping you.

352
00:18:12,439 --> 00:18:13,719
But, He Qunfei,

353
00:18:14,359 --> 00:18:16,199
