361
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,800
Please wait a little longer.

362
00:18:31,280 --> 00:18:33,640
Endless waiting.

363
00:18:34,839 --> 00:18:36,359
We've been together for so long,

364
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:38,439
and the words I've heard the most
is "wait".

365
00:18:39,359 --> 00:18:40,839
I waited three years ago,

366
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,599
and I'm still waiting.

367
00:18:42,719 --> 00:18:43,760
Qunfei,

368
00:18:44,199 --> 00:18:45,560
I'm really tired of waiting,

369
00:18:45,839 --> 00:18:47,199
and I've done enough waiting.

370
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,560
You can lend him the money.

371
00:18:51,319 --> 00:18:52,680
As long as you buy a house,

372
00:18:53,199 --> 00:18:54,920
I don't care even if you lend
200 million yuan to your dad.

373
00:19:03,239 --> 00:19:04,119
Siqi!

374
00:19:15,599 --> 00:19:16,880
While I'm abroad,

375
00:19:17,119 --> 00:19:18,760
please take care of everything for me,

376
00:19:19,439 --> 00:19:20,719
especially the Entertainment Center.

377
00:19:21,079 --> 00:19:21,800
If anything occurs,

378
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:22,959
call me immediately.

379
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:24,599
Ok.

380
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:26,520
Mr. Lei,

381
00:19:26,760 --> 00:19:27,880
