412
00:21:08,959 --> 00:21:10,479
My flight will leave at 10 am tomorrow.

413
00:21:16,199 --> 00:21:17,079
I'm leaving now.

414
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:30,199
Hello, Teacher Sun, long time no see!

415
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:47,119
Fine,

416
00:21:47,359 --> 00:21:48,640
I'll watch it now.

417
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:50,719
Ok.

418
00:23:02,239 --> 00:23:03,719
Mr. Lei, take your time
and have a good trip.

419
00:23:10,439 --> 00:23:12,439
Sir, please drive faster.

420
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,400
Are you in a hurry?

421
00:23:15,239 --> 00:23:16,439
You should have come out earlier

422
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:18,239
when you go to the airport at this time.

423
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:23,920
