00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:54,000
I mean that all of us have reasons
to believe that,

485
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:57,520
if S.G. is willing to invest

486
00:28:57,719 --> 00:28:59,239
and cooperate with us,

487
00:28:59,839 --> 00:29:03,359
