and interests as well.

489
00:29:08,839 --> 00:29:11,160
Lei, I have to say

490
00:29:11,319 --> 00:29:13,479
I am very interested in this project,

491
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:16,160
and I look forward
to cooperating with you.

492
00:29:16,719 --> 00:29:17,560
Fantastic.

493
00:29:21,280 --> 00:29:22,280
Here is the deal.

494
00:29:22,479 --> 00:29:24,199
Look forward to working with S.G.

495
00:29:25,040 --> 00:29:26,680
I have to go to Shanghai with you, then.

496
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,359
It's definitely my treat.

497
00:29:28,359 --> 00:29:30,280
You have to taste the Shanghai buns.

498
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:31,479
