525
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:46,839
I know that

526
00:31:47,359 --> 00:31:48,839
you have some prejudice against me.

527
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,119
But I believe that

528
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:53,079
