529
00:31:54,040 --> 00:31:55,319
I also believe that

530
00:31:57,479 --> 00:31:58,880
you won't regret it.

531
00:31:59,439 --> 00:32:02,000
Fanlv, give me a chance.

532
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:04,280
Let me protect you.

533
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:14,000
Mr. He and Miss Zou,

534
00:32:14,199 --> 00:32:15,000
congratulations.

535
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:17,119
You have already pre-purchased
the house.

536
00:32:17,239 --> 00:32:18,760
